    <body>
      <div xml:id="NA218-kiḷavi">
        <p type="edition">itu varaiviṭai melinta talaimakaḷ vaṉpoṟai (ER, ET: vaṉpuṟai) etirmoḻintatu.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">This is how SHE who had become weak in the time [before?] the marriage was desolate in the face of consolation.</p>
      </div>
      <div xml:id="NA218">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>            ñāyiṟu ñāṉṟu katirmaḻuṅ kiṉṟē</l>
<l>            yelliyum, pūvī koṭiyiṟ pulampaṭain taṉṟē</l>
<l>            vāvalum vayiṉṟoṟum paṟakkuñ cēvalu</l>
<l>            nakaivāyk koḷīi nakutoṟum viḷikku</l>
<l>            māyāk kātalō ṭataṟpaṭat teḷittōr </l>
<l>            kūṟiya paruvaṅ kaḻintaṉṟu pāriya</l>
<l>            parārai vēmpiṉ paṭuciṉai yirunta</l>
<l>            kurāaṟ kūkaiyu mirāa vicaikku</l>
<l>            māṉā nōyaṭa varunti yaṉṟun</l>
<l>            tamiyēṉ kēṭkuveṉ kollō </l>
<l>            pariyaraip peṇṇai yaṉṟiṟ kuralē.</l>
            </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>With the sun declining [its] rays have become blunt.</l>
<l>And with night</l>
<l>loneliness has settled on the creepers in full bloom.</l>
<l>And the bats fly on every side.</l>
<l rend="indent4">And the cock</l>
<l>calls whenever it smiles, making the mouth take a smile.(?)<note place="foot">What is the kind of cock referred to here? What is meant by this smile?</note></l>
<l>The season he talked of, making clear that it would happen,</l>
<l>with unfailing love, has passed by.</l>
<l rend="indent4">And the tawny owl,</l>
<l rend="indent">perched on the way-giving branch of the Neem tree</l>
<l>with broad trunk is sounding at night.</l>
<l rend="indent">And besides suffering so as to be killed by unending pain</l>
<l>I who am alone, will I hear</l>
<l rend="indent">the voice of the Aṉṟil in the large-trunked palmyra tree?</l>
<lg type="alternate" sameAs="2b">
    <l>And with night</l>
    <l>loneliness has settled like a creeper with flowers perishing<note place="foot">Thus T.V.G.’s interpretation.</note></l>
</lg>
        </lg>
      </div>
